{"id":260869,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/11/维权网-贵州桐梓县村民黄明海逃脱当地政府的抓/","date":"2012-11-03T10:45:57Z","modified":"2012-11-03T10:45:57Z","title":"维权网 | 贵州桐梓县村民黄明海逃脱当地政府的抓捕（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员陈华报道）因反对政府建煤化工厂强征、强拆而上访的贵州桐梓县燎原镇油草村民黄明海，被当地政府全程监控后，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日</span><span>又遭追捕，冲出重围后在山坡上露宿。前几天，政府官员告知黄明海：他和香港人权组织反党反国的人联系，他们已经查到，而且发出去的材料已被中央国安拦截。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2007</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月，贵州省发改委批准立项在燎原镇上马煤化工厂，占地</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">941</span><span>亩。</span><span>桐梓县成立煤化工厂修建指挥部，进行拆迁工作。﹙成立指挥部，违反</span><span>黔府发“</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2006</span><span>”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>号文件精神﹚。在拆迁中，采用施放催泪瓦斯、被精神病、关押、毒打、甚至致人死亡等暴力恐怖手段，</span><span>强征、强拆两千多亩土地。</span><span>凡是不搬迁和反对违法占地的村民都受到打击。很多村民在家里和路上被带走拘留，且不出具任何手续。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>黄明海等拆迁户向市、县法院起诉违法占地暴力拆迁残酷血腥打击农民。几次三番，法院都不予立案。</span><span>几年来，被强征、强拆的农民多次到市、省、中央上访均无结果。在北京上访还被</span><span>安元鼎黑保安抓起来关押在派出所殴打。现在，</span><span>油草村一千多人居无定所，衣食无着，很多人以乞讨为生。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>煤化工厂在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年建成，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年正式投产。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>黄明海电话</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 18798674810</span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-sGph5cRmsW8/UJTu1Xh9vdI/AAAAAAAAStI/Kx5ygq-0oNo/s1600/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE00.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"247\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-sGph5cRmsW8/UJTu1Xh9vdI/AAAAAAAAStI/Kx5ygq-0oNo/s320/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE00.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-7bnGGicgXE0/UJTu5o_eT9I/AAAAAAAAStQ/fRpvLhHfiT4/s1600/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE01.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"234\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-7bnGGicgXE0/UJTu5o_eT9I/AAAAAAAAStQ/fRpvLhHfiT4/s320/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE01.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-k2MTHjGCEuo/UJTu8Kd4EMI/AAAAAAAAStY/lozGnl9N5Yg/s1600/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE02.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"244\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-k2MTHjGCEuo/UJTu8Kd4EMI/AAAAAAAAStY/lozGnl9N5Yg/s320/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE02.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-8848750096426189747?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}